snippet.title: Yooka-Replaylee | Console Announcement Trailer!
snippet.description:
Yes! Yooka-Replaylee is coming to consoles! Peek the new gameplay trailer to celebrate!

PC: https://bit.ly/4e1LeBY
PS5: https://bit.ly/4e2rb6l
Xbox: https://bit.ly/4e5fkV4

Yooka-Replaylee is the remastered/remade, gorgeous, definitive version of Yooka-Laylee! A 3D-Platforming love letter to 3D-Platformers of old!

Join dymanic duo Yooka and Laylee as they venture out across beautiful, varied worlds in a bid to put an end to Capital B's nasty plan!

With improved graphics, more dynamic worlds, new and improved challenges, new collectibles, new characters, a whole host of quality of life improvements and more to discover!
